3.3pt; line-height: 170%;\"><span style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: '굴림체'; line-height: 170%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;○ 용역기간 : 계약일로부터 8개월 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"text-indent: 3.3pt; line-height: 170%;\"><span style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: '굴림체'; line-height: 170%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;○ 과업내용 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"text-indent: 3.3pt; line-height: 170%;\"><span style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: '굴림체'; line-height: 170%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- 한강 낚시전용공간 현황 및 이용실태 체계적 조사·분석</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"text-indent: 3.3pt; line-height: 170%;\"><span style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: '굴림체'; line-height: 170%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- 수환경변화, 한강버스 운항 등 낚시환경 영향요인 조사 및 정량·정성 분석</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"text-indent: 3.3pt; line-height: 170%;\"><span style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: '굴림체'; line-height: 170%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- 공간 개선 및 재구성 필요성 검토</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"text-indent: 3.3pt; line-height: 170%;\"><span style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: '굴림체'; line-height: 170%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- 신규 낚시 전용공간 조성 필요성 검토 및 후보지, 신규시설 구성안 제안</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"text-indent: 3.3pt; line-height: 180%;\"><span style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: '굴림체'; line-height: 180%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- 단계별 추진방향 및 운영·관리 개선사항 제시</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"text-indent: 3.3pt; line-height: 170%;\"><span style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: '굴림체'; line-height: 170%;\">&nbsp;나. 제안서 평가위원(후보자) 신청방법</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"text-indent: 3.3pt; line-height: 170%;\"><span style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: '굴림체'; line-height: 170%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;○ 신청기한 : </span><span style=\"position: relati